title: Oud Geld
overview: The "Bussink Bank", a small but renown family bank has been owned by the Bussink Family since 1860. But when the bank is partially taken over by the international orrientated "HollandBank", it is the end of an era. The Bussink family has a hard time keeping it's head above the water in this modern time as traditions disappear and the banking business gets more aggressive...
